Each of the files in this directory is a test program that will be parsed to
test the loop detector functionality by unit/dispatch_loop_detector.cpp.

The entire file is a single literal string, written in the C++ raw string
format---i.e., starting with R"<delimiter>( and ending with)<delimiter>". The
delimiter in this case is the word "dispatch". These literal strings get
included into the unit test and assigned to variables, which are then used as
normal strings.
